ðŸš€ Quickstart

To download all datasets (1979â€“2024), including ERA5 if configured:

python download_data.py --quickstart


or simply:

python download_data.py


To run without ERA5:

python download_data.py --all --years 1979-2024


ERA5 requires a free Copernicus Data Store (CDS) API key:

Create an account: https://cds.climate.copernicus.eu/register

Save credentials to C:\Users\<username>\.cdsapirc (Windows) or ~/.cdsapirc (macOS/Linux).

